    "description": "The Real Estate Service Act of the Philippines or Republic Act No. 9646. This course will tackle the basics and the acts that focus primarily its Implementing Rules and Regulations. After taking this module, you will be able to fully understand the use and importance of the RESA law in the real estate industry.  The course will use webinar videos and a Powerpoint presentation.  In order to assess this module, an online quiz and end of the module assignment will be given to the students.",
